Package: vDiversityRest
Type: Package
Title: Evaluate Diversity, Richness and Structure in Tropical Forests
Version: 0.6.0
Author: Andres Felipe Santos Lozano
Maintainer: Andres Felipe Santos Lozano <andresfesantos@gmail.com>
Description: This tool calculate the Importance Value Index (IVI), Margalef, Menhinick, Shannon-Wiener, Simpson and Berger Parker. Also measures beta diversity between ecosystems.
